 {"id":"git_safety_guard-3w5","title":"[PACK] platform.github - GitHub Platform Pack","description":"# GitHub Platform Pack (Non-CI Operations)

## Scope Clarification
This pack covers GitHub **platform-wide** operations that are NOT covered by `cicd.github_actions`:
- Repository management (delete, archive)
- Releases and assets
- Deploy keys
- Webhooks  
- Collaborators
- Branch protection

**The `cicd.github_actions` pack (already implemented) covers:**
- Secrets (`gh secret`)
- Variables (`gh variable`)  
- Workflows (`gh workflow`)
- Runs (`gh run`)

## Destructive Patterns (Platform-specific, NOT in cicd pack)

### Repository Operations
- `gh repo delete` - Repository deletion
- `gh repo archive` - Archive repository

### Release Operations
- `gh release delete` - Deletes releases
- `gh release delete-asset` - Deletes release assets

### Deploy Keys
- `gh repo deploy-key delete` - Removes deploy keys

### Webhooks
- `gh api -X DELETE repos/.../hooks/` - Webhook deletion

### Collaborators
- `gh api -X DELETE repos/.../collaborators/` - Remove collaborators

### Branch Protection
- `gh api -X DELETE repos/.../branches/.../protection` - Remove protection

## Safe Patterns
- `gh repo view`, `gh repo list`, `gh repo clone`
- `gh release list`, `gh release view`
- `gh pr list`, `gh pr view`, `gh pr create`
- `gh issue list`, `gh issue view`
- `gh api` with GET method

## Implementation Notes
- Parent category: platform.github (git_safety_guard-dxs)
- Keywords: gh
- IMPORTANT: Do NOT duplicate patterns from cicd.github_actions

